>About Jan</h1></header><p>Jan turns computers into thinking machines to ch=
ange how we use them.
Jan is created and maintained by Jan Labs, a robotics company.</p>
<p>With Jan, you can:</p>
<ul>
<li>Run <a href=3D"https://huggingface.co/models?pipeline_tag=3Dtext-genera=
tion" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer">open-source LLMs</a> lo=
cally or connect to cloud AIs like <a href=3D"https://openai.com/blog/opena=
i-api" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer">ChatGPT</a> or <a href=
=3D"https://ai.google.dev/" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer">G=
oogle</a>.</li>
<li>Fine-tune AI with specific knowledge.</li>
<li>Supercharge your productivity by leveraging AI.</li>
<li>Search the web and databases.</li>
<li>Integrate AI with everyday tools to work on your behalf (with permissio=
n).</li>
<li>Customize and add features with Extensions.</li>
</ul>
